HEADWORD: Ectental
<hw>Ec*ten"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>'ekto`s</grk> outside + <?/ inside.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld>
